tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE quantum_data_samples (
    sample_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    feature_1 FLOAT,
    feature_2 FLOAT,
    feature_3 FLOAT,
    quantum_class VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE quantum_data_samples (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    sample_name VARCHAR(255),
    qubit_count INT,
    measurement_result VARCHAR(50),
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE feature_engineering_tasks (
    task_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    task_description TEXT,
    qubits_used INT,
    task_status VARCHAR(20),
    task_completed BOOLEAN
);
